import React from "react";

const TableList = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <TableRow>
                <TableCell>1</TableCell>
                <TableCell>Akalesh Tanwer</TableCell>
                <TableCell>akalesh.aurasoft@gmail.com</TableCell>
                <TableCell>
                    <Tooltip title='view' arrow>
                        <IconButton size="small">
                            <VisibilitySharp color='primary' />
                        </IconButton>
                    </Tooltip>
                    <Tooltip title='view' arrow>

                        <IconButton size="small">
                            <EditSharp />
                        </IconButton>
                    </Tooltip>

                    <Tooltip title='view' arrow>

                        <IconButton size="small">
                            <DeleteSharp color='error' />
                        </IconButton>
                    </Tooltip>

                </TableCell>
            </TableRow>
        </>
    );
};

export default TableList;
